restaurant.name: Cafe Espanol
restaurant.description: Cafe Espanol offers patrons a wide variety of authentic Spanish cuisine. Specialty items include paella flavored with real wild saffron, imported Spanish manchego cheese, and Serrano ham or imported pulpo. All of these high-quality ingredients come together to give the diner the best possible tapas experience! Order a variety of small plates to sample at home or share with friends.

restaurant.name: Ditch Plains
restaurant.description: This sleek restaurant features high-quality seafood shack fare and comfort classics with a twist. Definitely try some fish or steak dishes, but save room for dessert! restaurant.name: Atlas Cafe & Bakery

restaurant.name: Grand Sichuan

restaurant.name: Salon de Tapas

restaurant.name: Prince St. Cafe & Catering Co.
restaurant.description: This cafe's extensive menu features unique international touches. Prince St. Cafe & Catering Co. is sure to have an innovative dish whether you're in the mood for breakfast, a hearty soup, a light pastry, pasta, or a sandwich.

restaurant.name: Tapas on Carmine
restaurant.description: Tapas on Carmine offers patrons a wide variety of authentic Spanish cuisine. restaurant.name: Jaya Malaysian
restaurant.description: Malaysia is a melting pot of rich and different cultures resulting in its exciting cross-cultural cuisine of traditional Malay, Indian, Indonesian, Thai and Chinese influences. No wonder customers who try Tanti Baci order again and again!

restaurant.name: Grand Sichuan

restaurant.name: Excellent Dumpling House

restaurant.name: The Sullivan Bistro (formerly the Sullivan Diner)

Experience the tantalizing aroma and sublime flavor of this real Italian specialty pizza in New York City! Winner, Best Pizza in New York via the Food Network, three years running.

Make a donation to City Harvest with a Delivery.com order! You can help those in need by choosing items from the City Harvest menu.
